<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP3">
<l>manti pāyvaṭa vēṅkaṭa māmalai vāṉavarkaḷ</l>
<l>canti ceyyaniṉ ṟāṉaraṅ kattara viṉaṇaiyā</l>
<l>ṉanti pōṉiṟat tāṭaiyu mataṉmē layaṉaip paṭaitta tōreḻi</l>
<l>lunti mēlataṉ ṟōvaṭi yēṉuḷḷat tiṉṉuyirē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sweet life inside of me, a servant, is [fixed], is it not,</l>
<l>on the clothes of a twilight-like hue and on the navel above [them],</l>
<l rend="indent">which has the unique beauty of having created Aja,</l>
<l>of Him on the serpent-bed in Raṅgam, who stood, so that the celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">worshipped,</l>
<l>on the great mountain of Vēṅkaṭam in the North with leaping monkeys.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
